Nafissatou "Nafi" Thiam (pronunciation French: ​[tʃam]; amụrụ 19 Ọgọst 1994) bụ onye na-eme egwuregwu Belgium ọkachamara na asọmpi mmemme ọtụtụ
Thiam bụ onye nwetere ọla edo Olympic ugboro abụọ, na-emeri mmemme heptathlon na 2016 na 2020 Summer Olympics

Ọ bụ naanị onye na-eme egwuregwu Belgian, nwoke ma ọ bụ nwanyị, gbachitere asọmpi Olympic nke ọma yana naanị nwanyị nke abụọ mgbe Jackie Joyner-Kersee nwetagoro mmeri azụ na azụ Olympic na ihe omume ahụ.
